### Cookbook

+ Tapenade
  + Black Olives (4 parts)
  + Capers (1 part)
  + Garlic cloves (2)
  + Challote (?)
  + Roasted Red Pepper (?)
  + Olive oil (3 parts)
  + Vinegar (1 part)
  + Lemon Juice (1 part)
  + Thyme
  + Basil
  + Parsley
  + S&P
  + Dijon (1 tbsp)

+ Salad of Decadence (for 1 person)
  + 1 Tomato, sliced in half cm cubes
  + 1/3 Green Bell Pepper, in super thin Julianne (1mm x 2cm)
  + 1/2 Red Onion, super thin sliced (1mm)
  + 1 medium leek, super thin sliced (1mm)
  + 2/3 sq cm Ginger, super thin sliced (1mm)
  + Tuna, half a can
  + Pategras, half cm cubes
  + Sardo, sliced
  + Dressing:
    + 2 tbsp Olive Oil
    + 1 tbsp Wine Vinegar
    + 1 tbsp Lemon
    + 1/2 tbsp Dijon (Maille!)
    + Oregano
    + Aji molido, generous
    + Parsley
    + Dried garlic
    + Chili flakes
    + Tabasco (Jalapeno), 7-10 drops
    + Generous Pepper (coarse ground Black Malabar)
    + Generous Salt
